<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" class="lfaq">
  <div class="l-section-header">
    <span class="l-eyebrow">Questions</span>
    <h2 class="l-section-h2">Frequently Asked</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="lfaq-list">

    <div class="lfaq-item">
      <button class="lfaq-q">How long does shipping take?<span class="lfaq-icon"></span></button>
      <div class="lfaq-a"><p>Orders are processed within 1&ndash;2 business days. Estimated delivery: US &amp; Canada 8&ndash;12 business days; UK 10&ndash;14 days; EU 11&ndash;16 days; rest of world 14&ndash;21 days. A tracking number is emailed within 2&ndash;4 days of dispatch.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lfaq-item">
      <button class="lfaq-q">What is the return policy?<span class="lfaq-icon"></span></button>
      <div class="lfaq-a"><p>Full refund within 30 days of delivery. For hygiene reasons, used masks cannot be returned unless defective. If your item arrives damaged or fails to power on, email a photo within 48 hours and we will send a replacement or full refund &mdash; no return required.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lfaq-item">
      <button class="lfaq-q">Is it safe for all skin types?<span class="lfaq-icon"></span></button>
      <div class="lfaq-a"><p>LUM&Egrave;RA masks are designed for general skin wellness use. If you have photosensitivity conditions, are taking photosensitising medications, or have any active skin condition, consult a qualified healthcare professional before use. Never look directly at the LED lights during use. Full safety instructions are included with each mask.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lfaq-item">
      <button class="lfaq-q">What certifications does the mask have?<span class="lfaq-icon"></span></button>
      <div class="lfaq-a"><p>LUM&Egrave;RA LED masks are CE, FCC, and RoHS certified consumer wellness devices. These are not FDA-cleared medical devices and make no medical claims. Certification documentation is available upon request.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lfaq-item">
      <button class="lfaq-q">How often should I use the mask?<span class="lfaq-icon"></span></button>
      <div class="lfaq-a"><p>We recommend 15-minute sessions, 3&ndash;5 times per week as a starting point. The mask auto-shuts off at 15 minutes. Daily use is fine for healthy adult skin. Consistency over time is what matters most.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lfaq-item">
      <button class="lfaq-q">What is the difference between the three masks?<span class="lfaq-icon"></span></button>
      <div class="lfaq-a"><p>All three share the same full-face skin-safe silicone design and USB-C charging. The Prestige includes all 7 colour modes plus 850nm near-infrared (450 LEDs). The Aura includes 850nm near-infrared with 5 colour modes (360 LEDs). The Spectrum is the entry model with 3 colour modes, no near-infrared (360 LEDs).</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lfaq-item">
      <button class="lfaq-q">How do I charge the mask?<span class="lfaq-icon"></span></button>
      <div class="lfaq-a"><p>The mask charges via USB-C cable (included). A full charge takes approximately 2 hours and provides multiple 15-minute sessions. The indicator light shows charging status.</p></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<script>
(function(){
  document.querySelectorAll('.lfaq-q').forEach(function(btn){
    btn.addEventListener('click',function(){
      var item = btn.closest('.lfaq-item');
      var wasOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
      document.querySelectorAll('.lfaq-item.open').forEach(function(el){el.classList.remove('open');});
      if(!wasOpen) item.classList.add('open');
    });
  });
})();
</script>

